data.details:
Cookie Biz- DB
Grades: K, 1, 2, 3

Want to be a #cookieboss this Girl Scout Cookie Program season? Join us for a Cookie Biz workshop; you will have the opportunity to work on the requirements for a Cookie Business or Financial Literacy badge. Through fun activities, you will also refine your goal setting, decision making, money management, business ethics and people skills that will be help you set up for success in the 2016 Cookie Sale. Girl Scout Daisies will earn the Count It Up Leaf and Brownies will earn the Meet My Customers Badge. 

*This event is for 2016 registered Girl Scouts, and registered & approved adult volunteers.
*For safety and supervision reasons, troops and individuals are not permitted to bring non-Girl Scouts or siblings.

$7/girl, $1/adult
Contact: Brittany McCallister 904.389.3071
